  <section>
    <h2>About This Project</h2>
    <p>
      This project focuses on detecting tumors in MRI scans using MATLAB.
      It highlights high-intensity regions, provides tumor staging, and
      improves accessibility with text-to-speech support for visually
      impaired users.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Tumor Detection</h3>
        <p>Detects bright intensity tumor regions using image processing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Comparision</h3>
        <p>Classifies tumor stage based on area and pixel intensity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Accessibility</h3>
        <p>Text-to-speech support for visually impaired users.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

